query: UPDATE tracks SET title = 'The Price of the Pulpit (Part 2)' WHERE `index` = 4 AND title = 'The Price of the Pulpit' AND albumId IN (SELECT albumId FROM (SELECT albumId FROM tracks WHERE title = 'The Price of the Pulpit' GROUP BY albumId HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AS temp) LIMIT 1
